---
permalink: "meet-our-team/{{person.short_name | slug}}/"
layout: default
pagination:
  data: collections.people
  size: 1
  alias: person
eleventyComputed:
  title: "{{person.name}}"
---

<div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto mt-16 px-8 flex-col space-y-16">
  <div>
    {% if person.image %}
      <img src="{{person.image}}" alt="{{person.name}}"  class="w-full h-auto shadow-lg rounded-lg" />
    {% else %}
      <div class="w-full flex justify-center">
        <svg class="w-2/3 text-primary-300" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" aria-hidden="true">
          <path clip-rule="evenodd" fill-rule="evenodd" d="M18 10a8 8 0 11-16 0 8 8 0 0116 0zm-5.5-2.5a2.5 2.5 0 11-5 0 2.5 2.5 0 015 0zM10 12a5.99 5.99 0 00-4.793 2.39A6.483 6.483 0 0010 16.5a6.483 6.483 0 004.793-2.11A5.99 5.99 0 0010 12z"></path>
        </svg>
      </div>
    {% endif %}
  </div>
  <div>
    <div class="prose lg:prose-lg">
      {{person.body | markdown | safe}}
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="relative my-16 px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
  <div class="prose prose-lg lg:text-xl text-gray-500 mx-auto">
    <p>
      Working with us also always includes contact with partners as we seek
      to give you the best outcomes possible.
    </p>
    <p>
      We work tirelessly to ensure the best outcomes for our clients. Ready to
      see what the accountants and staff at <b>Buckley &amp; Sitzman, LLP</b>
      can do for you and your business?
    </p>
  </div>
  <div class="max-w-prose text-center mx-auto">
    <p class="mt-10">
      <a
        href="/meet-our-team"
        class="inline-flex text-black items-center uppercase py-3 px-4 rounded-md
               hover:bg-secondary-600 bg-secondary-500 font-medium
               focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-offset-2
               focus:ring-secondary-400 focus:ring-offset-gray-900"
      >
        Meet the Rest of Our Team
      </a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div>
